description.value: The Rainswell is surrounded by a thick foggy mist. Creatures in within a 15 foot aura are @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Concealed]{Concealed}. This cloud is suppressed if the Rainswell fails a saving throw against a spell or effect with the Fire or Air keyword. If the aura is dispersed, it returns automatically at the end of the Rainswell's turn.
The Rainswells Aura of Mist becomes freezing cold. Enemies in the aura must make a DC 25 Basic Fortitude Save take 3d8 Cold Damage.
